metadata.description:
Dininho is a 16-bit Super Mario World inspired platform Game, Speedrun style with a ranking system. Cute and colorful with original graphics, the game is carefully designed and programmed by a genius mind. Also available on Steam and Nintendo Switch.

This new version brings Dininho into the Web3 metaverse which introduces Dininho as a product available now on Web3. Not just that, Dininho strives to open up numerous possibilities of growth and future experiences/interactions.
metadata.name: Dininho #1
